    {
        "content": "<p>If we have the equivalence <code>(Œ± ‚•§ Œ≤ √ó Œ≥) ‚âÖ ((Œ± ‚•§ Œ≤) √ó (Œ± ‚•§ Œ≥))</code> then this should follow from uncurrying, applying <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/category_theory.whiskering_right\">docs#category_theory.whiskering_right</a>, applying this equivalence and then currying back.</p>",
