    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Actually I think the following should be added in <code>category_theory.products.basic</code>. What's a good name for it?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">X</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">√ó</span> <span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">X</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚âÖ</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">X.1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">X.2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">hom</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">ùüô</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">ùüô</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">inv</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">ùüô</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">ùüô</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
