    {
        "content": "<p>And the original desired construction can be achieved more directly as</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">category_theory.functor.currying</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span> <span class=\"n\">category_theory</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">variables</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≤</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≥</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ¥</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">category</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ±</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">category</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≤</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">category</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≥</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">category</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ¥</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">F</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≤</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚•§</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≥</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚•§</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ¥</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚•§</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≤</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚•§</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚•§</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≥</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚•§</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚•§</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ¥</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"n\">curry_obj</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">curry_obj</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">functor.prod'</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">uncurry.obj</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">category_theory.prod.fst</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">uncurry.obj</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">category_theory.prod.snd</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚ãô</span> <span class=\"n\">uncurry.obj</span> <span class=\"n\">F</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
